text: ProstemmaLaporte (1832) Essai Class. syst. Hémipt. (Sheet 1): 6, 12 (Mag. Zool., 2, Suppl.) is a genus of bugs in the family Nabidae, subfamily Prostemmatinae and tribe Prostemmatini. == Species == The following species are included: * Prostemma aeneicolle Stein, 1857 * Prostemma albimacula Stein, 1857 * Prostemma antipodes Kerzhner, 1990 * Prostemma australicum Kerzhner & Strommer, 1990 * Prostemma bicolor Rambur, 1839 * Prostemma carduelis Dohrn, 1858 * Prostemma concinnum Walker, 1873 * Prostemma fasciatum (Stal, 1873) * Prostemma guttula (Fabricius, 1787) * Prostemma hilgendorfii Stein, 1878 * Prostemma kiborti Jakovlev, 1889 * Prostemma oeningensis Heer, 1853 * Prostemma reuteri Kerzhner, 1990 * Prostemma sanguineum (Rossi, 1790) * Prostemma walkeri Kerzhner & Strommer, 1990 Note: Prostemma pallidiceps Stål, 1860 is a synonym of Pagasa pallidiceps (Stål, 1860) ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Heteroptera genera Category:Nabidae
title: Prostemma
